    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ひどい。
世界樹が枯れてるなんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How horrible... The World Tree is withered...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>これじゃマナが枯渇するのも無理ねぇな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Makes sense why the Mana is drying up, then.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あの黒い光、なにか関係あるのかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Could that black light be connected somehow?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わからねぇ。
光の中から出てきたあいつ……人間なのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dunno.
That thing that came outta the light... Is it human?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>とにかく行ってみよう！
せっかく来たのに
なにもしないで帰るなんて出来ないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Anyway, let's check it out!
We can't just go back now after
coming all this way without doing anything.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
